{"word":"ἐπαγγέλλω","slug":"ἐπαγγέλλω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπαγγέλλω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀγγέλλω\">ἀγγέλλω</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b>to promise <a href='B:480 14:11'>Mk 14:11</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> In <b><a href='B:550 3:19'>Gal 3:19</a></b> <el>ᾧ ἐπήγγελται</el> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> = for whom the promise took effect. —The primary component of commitment in ἐ. is apparent <b><a href='B:610 2:10'>1 Ti 2:10</a>; <a href='B:610 6:21'>6:21</a>,</b> where some such rendering as <b>lay claim to</b> or <b>profess</b> is required. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπαγγελία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπάγγελμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}